-- Toyota Is Sued by Allstate Over Acceleration-Related Claims
-- B y   E d v a r d   P e t t e r s s o n
-- 2010-10-04T19:34:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/allstate-sues-toyota-saying-carmaker-hid-sudden-acceleration-defects.html
Toyota Motor Corp. was sued by
Allstate Corp. over sudden-acceleration claims. Allstate said it
has paid $3 million in claims and that Toyota hid defects that
caused the accidents.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edvard Pettersson in Los Angeles at 
 epettersson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
